		   <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top">
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Tue, Jun 5th 11:37 AM 2001 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class=sm>IP: Logged</span> | <a class=sm href="/db/classes.html?class=2&mid=99167596784783&num=7&post=1&replyto=99175545099629"><img src=/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=11 width=17> Reply to this</a></a>   <a name=99175545099629></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id=>Anonymous</span></a><b><span id=></span></b>
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</nobr><br><br><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Agreed, you've picked a really bad class if you want to solo. On the other hand, you do have one of the most sought after classes for groups to those in the know. The faster mobs go down, the less mana will be needed per mob and therefore more mobs you can kill before having to worry about taking a break for medding problems. Minimizing downtime is the way to level quickly, and you're noticing what a b**** it is trying to do it on your own. Take yourself to CT in Ferrott, at your level that is an excellent place to learn grouping skills and really load up the exp. Once done there, you can try LGuk or some of the Kunark outdoor zones if that is more to your liking. I was doing a level every other day in LGuk, and hell levels are something I remember fondly compared to what a pita it is to level now. :) Manage your aggro effectively so the cleric/healer can concentrate on keeping your tank alive and go to work with BS and as good of ratio weapons as you can get your hands on. Just don't give up, you'll find that later on in the game everyone will want your services, and you'll also have imo one of the funnest classes in EQ to play.<br><br>Adso<br>55th Season Rogue<br>Intrepid<br>Tholuxe Paells</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >0 Replies</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><tr><td>
